Class Road

java.lang.Object
Road
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Road>
public class Road extends Object implements Comparable<Road>
This class represents a Road object. Its main purpose is to connect two Towns with a certain weight value acting as the Edges in a Graph of Towns. Most of the methods are simple getters and setters, with a few small overrides on methods like equals, compareTo, and toString
Author:
Evan Song
